<h3>Information for Hardware Vendors</h3>
If you wish to be listed on this page, send mail to
<a href="mailto:webmaster@debian.org">webmaster@debian.org</a>
providing the following information:
<ul>
<li>company name
<li>URL
<li>e-mail address
<li>phone number (if accept international orders, include international
dialing prefix)
<li>fax number (optional)
<li>country
<li>whether ship internationally
<li>snail mail address (optional)
</ul>
